OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FNantlle U-turn on 2p debt  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fthreat                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Governors of a school which said it    
OL,6, would refuse meals to pupils more than 
OL,7, 1p in debt have announced they will    
OL,8, review its payment system.             
OL,10,FYsgol Dyffryn Nantlle, in Penygroes,   
OL,11,FGwynedd, had told parents the decision 
OL,12,Fwas due to a deficit in the school     
OL,13,Fmeals budget.                          
OL,15,FBut it sparked anger, joined by        
OL,16,FManchester United footballer and       
OL,17,Fanti-poverty campaigner Marcus         
OL,18,FRashford.                              
OL,20,FGwynedd council has now apologised for 
OL,21,Fconcern caused by the letter's wording.
